Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, you listenin' to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't work yourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it hurts too much, get yourself the hell elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Live your life the way you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:31.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never would've guessed I'd be coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:38.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon Queen Echidna,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and the Four Great Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all right. They haven't seen through my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Keep going, get even closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Closer, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Tis I, former Hero Leo Demonhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm here to interview for a position\Nin the Demon Queen's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm a skilled swordsman and have mastered all\Narcane schools of magic, including black magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've even defeated the Demon Queen\NEchidna herself in single combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am ready and raring to fight for your cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'm well aware of your army's current situation:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,your extreme lacking of numbers has\Nmade recovery nigh-impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do I know this? Because I was\Nthe one who decimated your army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But let's forget the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and instead, focus on the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The time has come to set off towards\Na brighter, more hopeful tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Together, let us bring ruin to those foolish humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and create a glorious Demon Kingdom\Nto last a millennia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is why I want to be hired to join your army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nailed it. I've got this job in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?!\NWhy the HELL would we hire YOU?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you hire me, you'll have an asset\Nthat's incredibly powerful--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll make you the greatest Demon Queen there ever was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you still talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll help you rapidly expand your workfo--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:05.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Under my leadership, performance will skyrocket, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you tea, do all your photocopies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll clean the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if you hire me in the next twenty minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you'll receive a brand-new...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a minute to explain\Na bit more about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:23.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One year ago, the Demon Army,\Nunder the leadership of Queen Echidna,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,descended upon the human world in a surprise invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the King gave me a mission\Nto destroy the Demon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As such, I gathered a party of elite heroes\Nand set out from the Capital at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:40.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There was just one problem.\NI don't mean to brag, but I'm really powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:46.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm a Royal Knight. I've mastered every weapon\Nknown to man, not to mention sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And to be totally honest,\Nmy party members just got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had a mage who refused to learn\Nanything that wasn't a healing spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,a meathead soldier who didn't know jack about magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and an archer who was straight-up useless\Nwhen enemies got too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Still, I forged trusting bonds with that dead weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,used the powers of teamwork and\Nfriendship to take down enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and watched them fight about room\Nassignments every time we stopped at an inn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In the time I wasted with them,\NI could've saved the world five times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So in the end, I set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,defeated Queen Echidna by myself,\Nand decimated the Demon Army by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:25.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how freakin' powerful I am!\NThere's literally no reason for her not to hire me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Master Leo, perhaps you weren't given an offer\Nbecause she dislikes your demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I've turned over a new leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's a totally new leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Quiet down, Lily. Stop jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's literally no reason for her not to hire him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:47.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, let her be, Mernes.\NLily's just happy to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know it's late to be realizing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but you've got a real COLORFUL group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you have a topic to discuss,\Nthen come out with it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If Queen Echidna found out we were meeting with you,\Nshe'd burn the castle to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we're only meeting with you because\Neven AFTER you were thrown out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you came back and forced our hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me start with a little presentation, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd like to remind each of you just how powerful I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll admit that my demeanor can be problematic at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even so, the fact that I possessed the strength\Nto defeat all four of you on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,should be enough to immediately\Nqualify me for the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,By reminding each of you of\Nthe circumstances of your defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope to gain your vote of approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see! I most certainly can vouch for your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'd been far too long since someone\Nbested me in a fair, honest duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you LAUGHING about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:07:00.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, now, crossing swords with\Na powerful opponent is a delight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Master Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:06.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The first of the Four Generals I fought was this one here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:12.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Edvard, "The Red Roar", the Dragon General.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:24.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In terms of raw stats, he was\Nthe toughest one out of the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dragonfolk and their draconic scales\Nare ridiculously strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I'd had to fight him just with a sword,\Nwho knows how that might've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Luckily for me, he's the kind of idiot--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:46.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Er, NOBLE WARRIOR who charges in to attack\Nby himself, so the fight was way easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good grog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've a question for you, actually.\NWhy do you serve Queen Echidna, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're powerful enough to try\Nand take over the world yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I've never given it proper thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:10.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's 'cause I want to live the life of\Na proper swordsman, dueling worthy opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rulin' the land's a busy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get to spend as much time\Nwith my daughter Julietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear it, no sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've got a daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I actually feel quite bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:35.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you journeyed alone, then you must not have\Nany friends with whom to spend your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, you're one to talk, Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm one hundred percent sure\Nyou don't have any friends, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After I defeated Edvard, I fought this guy here:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes, "The Unseen Blade," the Shadowless General.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's a purportedly "deadly" young half-demon\Nwho was once with the Assasins' Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I say "purportedly", but when I fought him,\Nhis speed and strength were unmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Five more minutes and he might've bested me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately for him, I hadn't gone in there\Nto try and beat him in a contest of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:15.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I defended myself while casting an AOE spell,\NCrimson Comet, to blow him away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but the spell ended up destroying everything\Nin its radius, so both Mernes AND the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:22.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And honestly, I had a rougher time with the fight\NAFTER I'd defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Apparently the blast was so big, it took out\None of the town's protected historical sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened after that fight you had with\Nthe townspeople? Did you ever pay them ba--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,La la la, I can't hear you! You'll have to speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:43.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't hear ya! You'll have to speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:48.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo! Did I sound like you? Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After Mernes came THIS surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily, "The Ruthless Fang," the Beast General.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The way we met was completely ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I took shelter from the rain under a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:07.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and when I looked to the side,\Nshe was THERE, standing next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:13.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she had amnesia, no family,\Nno friends, and nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:18.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wasn't about to leave a little kid out there by\Nthemselves, so I took care of her for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:25.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But when she finally remembered who she was,\Nshe said she's the Beast General Lily. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:33.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd have to fight her eventually, so I sucked it up\Nand fought her, and won, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pretty, uh, easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:40.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Later, I'd learn that her tribe believes that\Nif someone strong defeats you in combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,they're the person you're destined to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why'd this have to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:53.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leo! When're you gonna marry me? C'mon, marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll marry you when you're just a little older, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna wait! I wanna marry you now! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:09.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The last of the Four I fought was Shutina,\N"The Almighty Mage," the Sorcerer General.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:13.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rumors told that she possessed far\Ngreater pools of mana than other succubi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and had mastered all types of sorceries,\Nincluding ancient and accursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:24.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Knowing that, I started our battle with the AOE spell\NStasis, which prevents casting altogether,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and challenged her in physical combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She was... embarrassingly weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:41.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After two minutes of light combat,\Nyou started sobbing for mercy. It's kinda sad, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm a mage! Of COURSE I'm no match\Nfor a hero in hand-to-hand combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, but a real professional would have a Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:53.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to have a Plan B\Nfor someone who can nullify all my spells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:58.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There literally isn't anyone in the world who\Ncan do that the split second they walk up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Except there is: me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Forget that! What is all this about, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you I was gonna give you a presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll admit, I did want to hear how\Nhe defeated the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It all happened so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:20.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you were by far the most\Nuseless of all of us, Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Poor Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Will you just get to the point already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:36.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you, a HERO, come to interview\Nfor a job with the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why do you even WANT to join the Demon Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to mess with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why I left my life of\Nfighting the Demon Army behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...and why I decided to defect and\Njoin the other side after so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After defeating you Four and Echnida herself,\NI returned to Renailles, the Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:22.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't greeted by throngs of cheering citizens,\Nor presented with a royal reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Instead, I was met with long stares and\Nsharp glares of shock, fear, and skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are we sure he's human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, he's a monster in human skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:39.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fear and worry spread like wildfire.\NThere was no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Word spread via letter, messenger pigeon,\Nmagic sending, and posters:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:51.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"The Hero Leo is a danger to us all."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow that man to wander free\Nthrough our fields and streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We must ensure he never wreaks destruction upon us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,by putting an end to that man--no, that MONSTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's right! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The new demon on the chopping block was me.\NThat was what humanity came to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:17.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The following days, I was accosted\Nby a group of assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:22.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe they were that stupid!\NI took out the Demon Queen all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did they really think I'd let some\Nhalf-rate assassins do me in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:30.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Some time after that, I was called to\Nthe palace to speak with the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was your actions that kept the Philosopher's Stone\Nsafe, and for that, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It pains me to make this decree,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:44.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but as the kingdom's protector, I cannot turn\Na blind eye to the concerns of my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Great Hero Leo,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hereby banish you from our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never forget, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that I have the utmost trust in your goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did I risk my life to protect this rotten world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:25.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did I fight tooth and nail against the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everything was suddenly so meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I never had a home or put down roots,\Nso I had nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All I could do was wander aimlessly\Nfrom village to village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you hear what the Demon Army's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're hiring, right? Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're actually trying to do it again, after getting\Ntheir asses handed to them by that hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'd think they learned their lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That Demon Queen Echidna isn't\Nthe sharpest tool in the shed, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure isn't. Only a matter of time\Nbefore we stop hearin' about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened to that thing'a yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I came to the conclusion that\Nthe only person who'd be willing to take me in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,was the Demon Army themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:23.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I stayed up all night working on my spiel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,putting together a fancy presentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then crossed the endless sands,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,scaled the treacherous mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,all to end up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:37.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If the world is hellbent on killing me,\Nthen I'll have to kill them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's why I want to work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well, Leo the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You poor, pitiful soul, who now knows\Nhe used and protected the wrong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I sense no falsehoods nor trickery\Nbehind your reasons to join with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I believe you are genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sorcerer General Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've definitely gotten over a big hurdle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You will be hired for a one-month trial period!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:28.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be your manager for that period,\Nand will evaluate your worthiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I expect you to produce results during\Nyour trial period, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if those results are unsatisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be thrown out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard. I'm pretty done with roughing it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:45.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And you must not let Queen Echidna\Nknow we've hired you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:51.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Use a magic item or spell to keep\Nyourself disguised at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You got it. So, are there any issues\Nyou've been dealing with as of late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our top priorities are bolstering our ranks,\Nrepairing the castle, and procuring weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:03.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After that, there's budgeting, improving\Nemployee benefits, and providing counseling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:06.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We also need to perform maintenance on\Nthe mana reactors, train any new recruits...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rebuilding an army is a lot of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And not just for Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got a lotta work to do, too, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop jumping, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've been helping with loj... lojistics?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:25.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like, getting supplies and stuff,\Nand it's been really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's SO much I gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know logistics are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the most VITAL part of any...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's the most vital,\Nand they asked ME to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cool? It's SO cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, it's even worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is all YOUR fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Calm down there, Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've gotta admit, it'll be a relief\Nto have Master Leo on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:06.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well. I can be calm. I'm calm, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's let bygones be bygones!\NGlad to have ya, Master Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Glad to have ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Same here. Thanks, Edvard and Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mernes. You good? I'm looking\Nforward to working with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you are able to produce worthy\Nresults during this trial period,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we will not cheapen your efforts\Nby bringing you in as an 'unpaid intern'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We, the Four Great Generals, will recommend\Nto Queen Echidna that you be hired officially.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I won't let you down, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:53.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're in dire need of people, especially those\Nwho know how to manage an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:57.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then those bolstered ranks need training.\NThere's a mountain of tasks on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're essentially rebuilding from zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're not just struggling,\Nthey're on the brink of closing up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:08.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I want need to talk to Echidna,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and ask her the question I've been\Npondering since that fateful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Q-Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You heard my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is an invasion, but we must\Navoid killing whenever possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Any territory we occupy must be ruled peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:28.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She forbids indiscriminate killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:33.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What cause is so important that\Nshe would cripple her army with such a ruling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why does she still refuse to leave\Nthe human world despite her utter defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:45.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you these questions and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Live your life the way you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, Echidna. I'll be a part\Nof your army before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And this is the story of how I did just that.
